old kid,who lives with his mother and brother in a trailer.He witnesses the suicide of a mafia lawyer,who tells him an explosive secret before he dies.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eA US senator is missing.Is he even alive and if not,where is the body ? Mark now knows something that both the FBI and the mafia are interested in finding out.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eAs the pressure on him increases,he succeeds in finding a female lawyer who specializes in helping abused children.Combined with Mark's own resourcefulness,will she be able to extricate him from the mess he finds himself in ?\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eFairly interesting,but as usual for Grisham, longish.","rating":3,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/49365462?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"grisham","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/49365462?shelf=grisham"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2045079158"},"likeCount":30,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":0,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.Es8P9RDvrFQst8wFx__A4A":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.Es8P9RDvrFQst8wFx__A4A","__typename":"Book"},"User:1383849":{"id":1383849,"__typename":"User","legacyId":1383849,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1226811925i/1383849._UX200_CR0,39,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":563,"viewableName":"Patrick","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/1383849-patrick","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":0},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.MuiijSLeRX9gGI63HL3MKQ":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.MuiijSLeRX9gGI63HL3MKQ","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.Es8P9RDvrFQst8wFx__A4A"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:1383849"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1624649952742,"createdAt":1266535283000,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1266882568000,"text":"The book tells of a boy who happens upon a mob lawyer who commits suicide. But before he commits suicide, he divulges information on where the body of the murdered Senator was hidden by his mob boss. Fearing reprisal by the mob or the FBI for lying, he hires a lawyer to get him out of this mess. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eI only slightly dislike this book because the premise of the book is weak. I could not get over the fact that the kid could have avoided the whole suspense by telling the FBI the truth about the body of the Senator. In that way, he and his immediate family could have gone into the Witness Protection Program and considering his mother's miserable job, the WPP would actually be step up from his current life. Also, his lawyer could have advised him to tell the FBI so the kid would be in WPP instead of a possible target of the mafia. The excitement of the book did not have purpose to it so this is the reason the book sucked.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eAnd what is wrong with Assistant Attorney General, he already knew the kid was not talking because he was scarred for his life and the life of his family so could he not cut a deal with the FBI to expedite the WPP?\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eWhat is wrong with the mother? Sure it would be a hastle to be in the WPP but their lives are already in danger! So, the WPP would actually be safer for them instead of having their identity known currently. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eThis is an idiotic and unbelievable plot.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eI guess the only redeeming quality about this book is the relationship between the kid and the 52 year old lawyer in which they both alternated being the adult in the relationship. For that, I will give this book 1.5.","rating":1,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1383849?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/90318614"},"likeCount":28,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":9,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.0GKhjngkEFsT6D1iU2XB1Q":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.0GKhjngkEFsT6D1iU2XB1Q","__typename":"Book"},"User:57725883":{"id":57725883,"__typename":"User","legacyId":57725883,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1557030750i/57725883._UX200_CR0,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":489,"viewableName":"Rob","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/57725883-rob","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":90},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.Ijx1zrVVhyOU52i3hw-mNQ":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.Ijx1zrVVhyOU52i3hw-mNQ","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.0GKhjngkEFsT6D1iU2XB1Q"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:57725883"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1643477712475,"createdAt":1557283910467,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1557284016490,"text":"This was a really terrific read, a great story line with some memorable characters.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eTwo young boys, brothers, are unwitting witnesses to a suicide. The older boy does all he can to stop the man from this act but to no avail. The man shoots himself in the head but before doing so he tells the young boys, Mark Sway, his reason for doing it. This information now marks Mark as a threat to the MOB. The FBI is desperate for Mark to reveal all he’s been told but after being threatened by the MOB to keep his mouth shut or his brother and mother will suffer Mark is terrified to say a word.\u003cbr /\u003eAt this point Mark gets Reggie Love, a defence lawyer, to protect him from all the law enforcement people and so protect him from the MOB. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eBetween Mark, who doesn’t lack for cunning and intelligence, and Reggie they manage to keep one step ahead of both the Mob and the FBI.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eThe Sway family started with nothing very much but now they have quite literally nothing at all. Their trailer home, along with all their personal effects, has been burned to the ground. It’s up to Reggie and Mark to keep everyone safe whilst trying to do the right thing and hopefully survive this ordeal.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eWhat follows is a very intense cat and mouse thriller.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eA highly readable tale. 4/5 stars.\u003cbr /\u003e","rating":4,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/57725883?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"stand-alone-thrillers","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/57725883?shelf=stand-alone-thrillers"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2321441344"},"likeCount":28,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":0,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:47521763":{"id":47521763,"__typename":"User","legacyId":47521763,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1642185536i/47521763._UY200_CR6,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":499,"viewableName":"Stephen Robert Collins","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/47521763-stephen-robert-collins","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":36},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.qlsl4-uP7N1PDcBfNvIb5g":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.qlsl4-uP7N1PDcBfNvIb5g","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.-p-fK_M3pJzaFA9H4LFp4A"},"creator":{"__ref